Astoria Boulevard, at the S. W. corner of 49th Street--the old Bowery Bay Road--showing the Queens County Hotel, built in 1873 by Mrs. Christian Scheurer and established as a hotel in 1875, with her son Wm. H. Scheurer as manager. The edge of St. Michaels Cemetery is on the extreme left.

View 2: April, 1925
Views 3,4: June 3, 1927

Views 1,2: Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
